<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真是越来越奇怪了！” 爱丽丝一边变大一边说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24569</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当她往下看时，她的脚已经看不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，我的脚！” 爱丽丝说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不知道谁可以帮你们穿上鞋子和袜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我将会离你们越来越远，再也帮不到你们了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接着，她担心了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果她的脚不听话了怎么办？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定要对它们好一点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每年圣诞节我都要给它们一双新靴子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是给我自己的脚送礼物好像很奇怪呢！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天啊，我在胡说八道什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，她的头碰到了大厅的天花板。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝继续变大，她已经超过了九英尺，但她并不伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，她可以很容易地够到玻璃桌上的金钥匙了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝拿起钥匙，迅速打开了花园的门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可怜的爱丽丝，她太大了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果她侧身躺下来，就可以用一只眼睛看到花园里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>至于进入花园，那就非常困难了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝又哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102338</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107901</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝试图责备自己，但却哭得更凶了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她流了一大堆眼泪，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117762</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>眼泪变成一个大水池，有四英寸深，淹了半个大厅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，爱丽丝听到远处传来脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她赶快擦干眼泪，看看是谁来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是那只白兔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他穿着外套，手里拿着白手套和扇子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在黑暗的大厅里边跑边自言自语：“公爵夫人！公爵夫人！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果我迟到了，她一定会非常生气的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝现在已经非常绝望了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156370</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她愿意向任何人寻求帮助，即使是一只会说话的兔子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她耐心地等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>直到兔子跑近，她才用轻柔的声音说：“不好意思……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>白兔吓了一大跳，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167688</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>扔掉了手里的手套和扇子，快速地跑进黑暗中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174431</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝捡起兔子的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为大厅很热，爱丽丝开始用扇子扇风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天的每一件事情都很奇怪。” 爱丽丝说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨天一切都还很正常。这一夜之间我是怎么变成这样的？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天早上我确实感觉有一点儿不同。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝继续扇扇子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许我变成了另外一个人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204643</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207176</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想起了她的朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她没有变成他们中的任何一个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210273</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝又大哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要是夏洛特能看到这个兔子洞，然后大喊我的名字该多好！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我实在不想再一个人待在这里了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她边说边看了一下自己的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的一只手居然已经戴上了兔子的手套。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是怎么戴上这只手套的呢？我一定又变小了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241528</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝跑回桌子，站在桌子旁边作对比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她觉得自己差不多有两英尺高。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且，她还在不断地变小！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一定是扇子。” 爱丽丝说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为了不让自己小到消失，她扔掉了扇子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真险啊！现在可以去花园了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝跑到花园门前，但是门又关上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爱丽丝没有钥匙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在大厅里找了找，发现钥匙在玻璃桌上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“钥匙是怎么到那里去的呢？” 爱丽丝绝望地看着它，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在比之前还要糟糕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我从来没有变得这么小过！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304259</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，爱丽丝的脚滑了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她掉进了一滩盐水里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>